|| 🪵 ModernWood – Furnix E-Commerce Website  ||

ModernWood (Furnix) is a **modern and responsive e-commerce platform  designed for premium wooden furniture.  
It allows users to explore, filter, and purchase products with a smooth and optimized experience.  

---

|| 🚀 Features  
- ✅ Modern & Responsive UI (Mobile + Desktop Friendly)  
- ✅ Product Catalog with Categories & Filters  
- ✅ Advanced Search & Sorting Options  
- ✅ Shopping Cart & Wishlist Management  
- ✅ Secure Checkout Process (Payment Gateway Ready)  
- ✅ User Authentication (Login / Signup / Profile Management)  
- ✅ Admin Dashboard (Product, Orders & Users Management)  
- ✅ Order Tracking System  
- ✅ SEO Optimized & Fast Loading  

---

|| 🛠️ Tech Stack  
- **Frontend:** React.js / Next.js, Tailwind CSS, Redux / Context API  
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js  
- **Database:** MongoDB / MySQL  
- **Authentication:** JWT / OAuth  
- **Deployment:** Vercel / Netlify (Frontend), Render / AWS / Heroku (Backend)  

--- 📂 Project Structure  
# Frontend
cd frontend
npm install

# Backend
cd ../backend
npm install

